Libhelper Tools 
===============

This directory contains a small toolset that uses libhelper. It serves both as an example of
how libhelper can be used, and some useful tools for working with macho files.


macho_split
----------

macho_split can be used to split a Universal Binary file containing multiple Mach-O's of diff
erent architectures. You can use it like so:

$ macho_split some_binary

It will produce a list of files in the format `macho_split0x.arch`. 


